/*!
@defgroup dcif DCIF: Display control Interface
@details The MCUXpresso SDK provides a peripheral driver for the Display control Interface

The DCIF supports multiple layers of input, each layer supports programmable plane size
and position, background color and alpha blend/Porter-duff blend, with RGB/compressed
input formats, and layer 1 and 2 also supports indexed/YUV input; supports 3 types of output
interface,  Parallel RGB(DPI), Display Bus Interface(DBI), and tx packet interface.

